<div class="container">
  <h1><strong>What Do I Do With...?</strong></h1>

  <p>Not sure what to do with items that arenâ€™t collected curbside? You've come to the right place!</p>

  <p>Every day, King County residents and businesses run across unwanted items that make them wonder: "What do I do with this?" This site was designed to answer that question! To begin, search by key word below or use the drop-down menu to select a general category. The following pages will ask for more information and allow you to narrow your selection.</p>

  <p>Have you ever bought a new appliance and wondered how to get rid of your old one? Found stacks of old business periodicals you want to recycle? Upgraded your organization's computers and ended up with a mountain of old electronic equipment? The "What Do I Do With...?" directory contains listings of hundreds of businesses and organizations that accept unwanted items from residents and businesses in King County, WA, for reuse, recycling, or proper disposal.</p>

  <hr>

  <%= form_tag do %>
    <div class="col-xs-3">
      <%= select_tag "material", options_from_collection_for_select(@materials, "id", "name"), prompt: "Select a category", class: "form-control input-sm select_box" %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-success search_button">GO</button>

  <div id="material_result">
  </div>

  <script id="material-result-template" type="text/x-handlebars-template">
